729672f-a.text:
Sneden Ave. (houses thereon), south side, east from Annadale Road to Barclay Ave. The view is southeastward across the tracks of
the Staten Island Railroad.
1924.
P. L. Sperr.
729672f-a.folder: Sneden Avenue & Annadale Road, Staten Island, NY

728341f-a.text:
(1)
Annadale Road, south of the S.E. corner of Sneden Ave. The two houses stand on the M. Rice property (1898 and 1907 maps).
May 4, 1926.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
A view of the first house seen in view 1, looking northward
toward Sneden Ave.
May 4, 1926.
P. L. Sperr.
